{"tid":1546000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵海外業務資產","createTime":"2019-09-06T06:17:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T08:13:25.000Z","uid":284627,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"56faff8a3ad79003a47d6ccbf5c8dec73256f1d8","tid":1546000,"uid":284627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:17:35.000Z","msg":"港共政府作為最大股東，要集結其他股東力量去迫黨鐵系無咩可能嫁啦....如果內部無人夠膽backup黨鐵既片，紀錄一定會消失<br />\n<br />\n點解唔多D用佢 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">海外業務資產</span></strong>去搞返黨鐵？<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">唔可以令佢地之前hard sell 自己有唔少海外業務既努力白白浪費！！！！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GXnJU3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GXnJU3.png&h=f29827b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsend 資料 - <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1.  831開放車站空間予不明黑衫人襲擊平民及疑似殺人，其他公司作為外地相關業務既持份者，一樣可以幫忙令真相公開<br />\n2. 公開黨鐵做過既<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好 事 </span></strong><br />\ne.g. 不斷拒絕負責鐵路日常運作；不斷無故關站；縱容不明人士入車卡打人...etc</div><br />\n<br />\n我地要集結同黨鐵有業務合作既公司，要求黨鐵回應事件，比外國勢力施加壓力<br />\n<strong>唔可以比 黨鐵 唔出聲私了</strong><br />\n亦要散播危機意識，到底黨鐵系甘無中立角色既私企，到處系海外投資拓展，到底對佢地國家/鐵路系統有幾大<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國家安全危機</span></strong>？<br />\n一定要引用例子cctv片直送警總，話比所有同佢合作既機構知 黨鐵系無道德同私隱標準既公司，系可以無法庭命令/批准下 實時send所有cctv 片段比執法機構，系一個可疑既間碟機構<br />\n<br />\n一定要比其他合作業務知道黨鐵D仆街野<br />\n無論今日外國勢力比唔比到壓力黨鐵都好，以後都唔好比佢甘好過，仲好似好巴閉去外國賺錢<br />\n只有對當地機構對黨鐵有一定程度信心不足，先可以令將來既合作機會告吹，先系對港鐵最大的報復<br />\n<br />\n返大西北食屎啦 黨鐵！"},{"pid":"7ac0c6cf85a25bc5db05a0e1f06adf4b15d2fab4","tid":1546000,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr3aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=eaa16557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"d34f17e59a15dcd66a2e3996e5f483fca65b0d1e","tid":1546000,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:18:40.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"681423cddf9f08b7c9ed2d0da8075fb997554696","tid":1546000,"uid":306999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a4726e323afe7f70f1307b832f252a3c8d659d","tid":1546000,"uid":284627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好放過 黨鐵 ！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>由MTR Corporation (Crossrail) Limited營運的倫敦伊利莎伯綫<br />\n由First MTR South Western Trains Limited 營運的英國西南部鐵路<br />\n由MTR Tunnelbanan AB營運的斯德哥爾摩地鐵<br />\n由MTR Express (Sweden) AB營運來往斯德哥爾摩與哥德堡的高速鐵路(MTR Express)<br />\n由MTR Pendelt&aring;gen AB 營運的Stockholms pendelt&aring;g<br />\n由Metro Trains Melbourne Pty. Ltd.營運的墨爾本都市鐵路<br />\n由Northwest Rapid Transit財團負責公私聯營的營運、列車及系統合約，並由Metro Trains Sydney Pty. Limited營運的悉尼西北鐵路綫</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9433fc7b73a3d00849b826f2a3c17e692032ec38","tid":1546000,"uid":306999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"跳閘post咁多人<br />\n呢啲